name: Space Diner - Art Demo
description:
Take a look at both version, thank you! Description -

A project that was made during school, in November 2021. It was a collaboration between me and 3 other students. v1 is the normal version of the scene, and v3 is the version with an eclipse blocking out the sun. v3 has more features but please try both out if you can! Thank you! - Team Lordran
